metadata.title: PETIMETI Wall Mount for EERO 6 Mesh WiFi System, Space Saving Wall Mount Bracket for EERO 6 Router with Cord Management and Easily Moved(3 Pack)
features: Perfectly Fit ---This outlet wall mount is specially designed for eero 6 mesh wifi system.
Excellent Cord Management ---This mount for eero 6 wifi uses the cord that comes with your eero 6 router, the cord groove allows simple storage of excess cable, great idea to save space.

Installation with No Holes or Tools Required ---Put the eero 6 mesh wifi router and power plug into the wall mount, then wrap the cord into groove. No need any tools or damage to your wall and finish in 5 minutes.
Easy to Move--- Your EERO 6 Router with this wall mount can easily be moved from room to room, unlike all the other mounts on the market which require permanent placement.
Clean Appearance---This Mount does not have any unnecessary embellishments.Looks clean and classic with your eero 6 Wifi.Great decoration for Living room, bedroom or other room.
description: Wall Mount for EERO 6 Mesh WIFI System

Hide the cord at the wall mount back cable groove and put the eero 6 router and power adapter together,make all looks clean.  Durable hard plastic material, sturdy enough and can hold the eero 6 router securely.  Easy to Install and replace, no need any tools to install and finish in 5 minutes.  Suitable for any position as long as there is a socket, enjoy wifi anywhere at home.
NOTE: EERO 6 ROUTER IS NOT INCLUDED!
